WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.798
Sixty percent of scam losses come from people over sixty.

00:00:04.938 --> 00:00:13.487
Care Mode is one switch. Bigger text. Simpler flow. Spoken verdicts.

00:00:13.627 --> 00:00:21.036
The home screen is just two buttons. Paste and check. Or call my family.

00:00:21.176 --> 00:00:28.459
When ScamRadar finds a scam, it doesn't just show a verdict. It reads it aloud.

00:00:28.599 --> 00:00:32.733
And the family pod hears about it the moment they need to.

00:00:32.873 --> 00:00:36.597
Built for the people who get the most scam calls.
